I thought I'd let the community know that JMeter has a new
JUnitSampler in the main CVS HEAD. My plan is to include it in 2.2
release in 2-3 months.

For those who want to try it out, tonight's nightly build will have
the JUnitSampler. feel free to send feedback to jmeter-user mailing
list or directly to my email.
